By":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:30:06.000Z","msg":"天生人類setting 係咁樣 負面情緒比正面情緒多 <br />\n用這樣就好了的心態去感受依個世界會容易d 過<br />\n加油啊大家都係你睇我好我睇你好，有苦自己知"},{"pid":"e4589cb79f4c368177a20bd5588f49a6ca1ff7d6","tid":2324213,"uid":305718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e9a77c7421b7ff84a9fc3f6a14df6b73ffbdec5","tid":2324213,"uid":301263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1045607390c275ef47f8d7ba4ec435eb9f29a64e","tid":2324213,"uid":249323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"271c929e2192e68dad5a0c98c4098227feaaf871","tid":2324213,"uid":301263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:21:48.000Z","msg":"我諗我係傻嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:23:36.000Z","msg":"傻豬 愛自己多啲 <br />\n唔好理人地點諗<br />\n早啲瞓啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:24:29.000Z","msg":"好啦 晚安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我再飲多杯就醉 可以訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:30:19.000Z","msg":"我都想飲 暖吓肚<br />\n咪飲到醉喇但係 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a1c837563eee1e7aad19a664502fa472bb1265","tid":2324213,"uid":305718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14dfa1802e0a21bf744af1924ecc305c9f9e469","tid":2324213,"uid":301263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:28:38.000Z","msg":"多謝大家 我飲埋呢杯酒就瞓 感覺好好多啦<br />\n我愛你地 可以取一刻暖真係好好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:31:56.000Z","msg":"掂啦 今晚嗰覺好好瞓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b5e389fa63b00f9b44a51e4a17ac915d9daea7","tid":2324213,"uid":86713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:50:55.000Z","msg":"生比死需要更大勇氣<br />\n今世嘅劫難都係考驗<br />\n放棄就要重新由第一關開始玩過<br />\n所有苦痛都要重新再經歷過<br />\n<br />\n我係咁樣鼓勵自己走出嚟 希望你加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f908fdbfc13437f436a6bdd508ec89dd4fdda307","tid":2324213,"uid":262647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d847c8acc889d7ec88df9ccd924b730582bbba5","tid":2324213,"uid":301263,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"03805f95584a01f6e039a579c709e78cc4cd5f36","tid":2324213,"uid":336922,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:08:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=45uSYC7335U&amp;list=PL5TQ1qOhiEMAw5trrgrIriNx6At2lFBTR&amp;index=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D45uSYC7335U%26list%3DPL5TQ1qOhiEMAw5trrgrIriNx6At2lFBTR%26index%3D3&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725JR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=da9eb5c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=45uSYC7335U&amp;list=PL5TQ1qOhiEMAw5trrgrIriNx6At2lFBTR&amp;index=3</a><br />\n僕が死のうと思ったのは／曾經我也想過一了百了"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:11:58.000Z","msg":"喊到傻 我岩岩一直聽中島美嘉演唱會個版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:56:15.000Z","msg":"識貨 師兄"},{"pid":"a93c2d50d8ad61e7ac7f741a412c139b59a7754f","tid":2324213,"uid":201975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:58:52.000Z","msg":"覺得自己諗嘢好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至唔至於死？未至於既<br />\n但係再咁樣落去如果有一日影響到珍重既人<br />\n一諗到有可能會有呢日<br />\n就好想死了"},{"pid":"d7649b8fb7b18fdc7ecd6444c5aafe87d223d1f4","tid":2324213,"uid":53769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T20:54:30.000Z","msg":"我明樓主講咩 我早個月都有呢個感覺<br />\n<br />\n今年失去太多野 唔知點算好<br />\n<br />\n懷疑自己開始精神受唔住 夜晚返到屋企坐喺到會想喊 透唔到氣咁<br />\n<br />\n想有意外可以帶走自己<br />\n<br />\n好彩得到朋友一點點既愛 雖然好多時都有好強既孤單感<br />\n<br />\n但係想消失既想法 減弱左小小 算暫時可以勉強支持住<br />\n<br />\n樓主不如都試吓做主動搵下身邊嘅人 那怕係小小時間可以分心下都好<br />\n<br />\n希望你可以振作"},{"pid":"7c0f0ed4b9aa22707f4193bd678a0f6accbcbe09","tid":2324213,"uid":305984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T21:14:52.000Z","msg":"唔好死住先啦 仲有好多美食未享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}